Just that alone,
how do you know?

00:25:00.830 --> 00:25:02.300
There's a few
thousand students who

00:25:02.300 --> 00:25:03.800
go through d.school,
maybe, a year--

00:25:03.800 --> 00:25:06.176
but how do you get to
