00:25:29.360 --> 00:25:31.120
because it's particularly bad.

00:25:31.120 --> 00:25:33.250
And then, OK, how does
that apply to the US?

00:25:33.250 --> 00:25:34.950
Because the US
thing-- we've been

00:25:34.950 --> 00:25:37.250
working in K-12 for a
