but nothing's that big a deal.

00:25:42.610 --> 00:25:46.827
And so trying to
scale by seeing what

00:25:46.827 --> 00:25:48.410
we can do as the
different experiments

00:25:48.410 --> 00:25:49.950
and then how you scale them.

00:25:49.950 --> 00:25:52.150
And so we're making progress.

00:25:52.150 --> 00:25:54.420
I mean, there's lots
